### RxDB: Synchronous Migration Strategy

Source: https://github.com/pubkey/rxdb/blob/master/docs/migration-schema.html

Demonstrates a synchronous migration strategy for RxDB collections. This strategy transforms data from a previous schema version to the current one by modifying the document object directly. If null is returned, the document is removed.

```javascript
myDatabase.addCollections({
  messages: {
    schema: messageSchemaV1,
    migrationStrategies: {
      // 1 means, this transforms data from version 0 to version 1
      1: function(oldDoc) {
        oldDoc.time = new Date(oldDoc.time).getTime(); // string to unix
        return oldDoc;
      }
    }
  }
});
```

