### Schema Migration with Document Filtering

Source: https://github.com/pubkey/rxdb/blob/master/docs-src/docs/migration-schema.md

Demonstrates how to use a migration strategy to filter documents, effectively removing old documents that do not meet certain criteria (e.g., older than a specific date) during schema migration.

```javascript
myDatabase.addCollections({
  messages: {
    schema: messageSchemaV1,
    migrationStrategies: {
      // 1 means, this transforms data from version 0 to version 1
      1: function(oldDoc){
        oldDoc.time = new Date(oldDoc.time).getTime(); // string to unix
        return oldDoc;
      },
      /**
       * this removes all documents older then 2017-02-12
       * they will not appear in the new collection
       */
      2: function(oldDoc){
        if(oldDoc.time < 1486940585) return null;
        else return oldDoc;
      }
    }
  }
});
```

