### RxDB: Asynchronous Migration Strategy

Source: https://github.com/pubkey/rxdb/blob/master/docs/migration-schema.html

Illustrates how to use asynchronous functions within RxDB migration strategies. These functions can perform operations like fetching data from an external API before returning the transformed document. The strategy returns a Promise that resolves with the new document data.

